responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "4C26A08C4735D1669FE36791A248629C", "The manifests provide information about where Sephilion hoards its secret riches. For those who can\'t detect magic, like your friend Sweeney, it would prove quite useful. I gave her the documents I had in exchange for her assistance with the Sighted. It\'s too bad it hadn\'t amounted to anything in the end. I advise you to turn back, and find your wits and common senses. Here, take this with you, it\'s what I have to repay you for your kindness.")
name: SQ_0121_NewAelaCorridor_StarvingMage_DLG_19_Response
